latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Protecting my skin from heat rashes, acne, tanning and maskne this summer with @aureana_skinscience’s 4 step summer skincare routine -

1. Purite Oil-Control Face Wash 
2. Essentiel Face Scrub
3. Essential Pore Minimizing Toner 
4. Purité Acne Dissolver Gel

You can get yours on Myntra, Amazon and www.theauworld.com

#Collaboration - I’ve always been a big @sadhev fan and now there is a new addition to the list of products I will repurchase from them. I tried their Ayurvedic Shampoo & Conditioner combo and here are my thoughts -

Sadhev’s Ayurvedic shampoo has a rich and creamy texture, lathers easily and leaves the hair smelling super fresh. It contains Bhringraj, Hibiscus & curry leaves and also balance the oil production on the scalp making it suitable for all hair types. 

Post shampoo I condition the ends with Sadhev’s Ayurvedic hair conditioner. It has a thick consistency and helps restoring the moisture in the raid reducing the frizz and making my hair manageable. It’s packed with goodness of Aloe Vera which is a natural conditioner, hibiscus & reetha

Sadhev Ayurvedic Shampoo followed by Ayurvedic Conditioner is my go to combo for healthy and shiny hair. 

Love,
Suks

#SkincareWithSadhev #ayurvedicshampoo #ayurvedicskincare
